                   densities of 310 $\pm$ 45 mJy for SrcI and 240 $\pm$
                   35 mJy for BN. SrcI is optically thick even at 229
                   GHz. No trace of the H30alpha recombination line is
                   seen in its spectrum, although the v 2 = 1,
                   5(5,0)-6(4,3) transition of H2O, 3450 K above the
